41
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:05,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>You!</i></font>

42
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:08,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>You made a fool of me...</i></font>

43
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:13,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>How dare you mock
my pirate blood?!</i></font>

44
00:02:13,070 --> 00:02:15,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>Stop it, Usopp!</i></font>

45
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:37,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Klahadore...</font>

46
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Are you there, Klahadore?</font>

47
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Klahadore...</font>

48
00:02:46,230 --> 00:02:48,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">M-Merry!</font>

49
00:02:48,820 --> 00:02:49,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Merry!</font>

50
00:02:50,690 --> 00:02:53,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What's wrong?! What happened?!</font>

51
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:54,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Open your eyes, Merry!</font>

52
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:57,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Please don't die!</font>

53
00:02:57,660 --> 00:02:59,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">M-Miss Kaya...</font>

54
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:01,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Thank goodness you're all right...</font>

55
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Merry...!</font>

56
00:03:07,290 --> 00:03:10,500
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Merry? Wh-Who did this?!</font>

57
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Klahadore!</font>

58
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:14,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">He... attacked me!</font>

59
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:21,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">He... He was a pirate all along!</font>

60
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:24,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Wh-What are you talking about...?</font>

61
00:03:24,810 --> 00:03:30,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">He only got close to you
so he could steal your estate...</font>

62
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Then...</font>

63
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:49,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">what Usopp said yesterday was true...</font>

64
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:53,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yes, come to think of it...</font>

65
00:03:54,210 --> 00:03:59,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">When he learned the truth,
he did his best to help us!</font>

66
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:05,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yet, not a single one of us
even tried to hear him out!</font>

67
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>You gotta run, Kaya!</i></font>

68
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>They're gonna kill you!</i></font>

69
00:04:11,610 --> 00:04:13,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><i>But you gotta escape for now!</i></font>

70
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:21,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We gave shelter to the true villain
while we spurned that brave lad!</font>

71
00:04:21,530 --> 00:04:26,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">He ran himself ragged
for the sake of the village...</font>

72
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:29,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">and we drove him away...!</font>

73
00:04:33,460 --> 00:04:36,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">S-Someone help! Merry is...!</font>

74
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:36,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82" color="#d6d6d6">Miss Kaya!</font>

75
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:37,970
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">It's no use...</font>

76
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:44,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">The rest of the staff has been
on leave since yesterday.</font>

77
00:04:45,010 --> 00:04:46,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">No...</font>

78
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Then I'll...</font>

79
00:04:47,930 --> 00:04:50,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You must remain calm!</font>

80
00:04:50,730 --> 00:04:53,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">They haven't enacted their plan yet!</font>

81
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:58,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You must think
things through carefully!</font>

82
00:04:58,030 --> 00:05:02,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">If Klahadore wants your
mansion and your fortune...</font>

83
00:05:02,370 --> 00:05:05,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">then just hand it over to him!</font>

84
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:08,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">None of it is worth risking your life!</font>

85
00:05:11,210 --> 00:05:12,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">You're right.</font>

86
00:05:12,580 --> 00:05:14,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cruel as it may be,</font>

87
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:17,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">you're the only one who
can stop Klahadore now.</font>

88
00:05:19,470 --> 00:05:21,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Can you do it?</font>

89
00:05:21,050 --> 00:05:24,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This isn't your responsibility, but...</font>

90
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:30,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Even I know this isn't just
something I can run away from...</font>

91
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:33,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I understand that fully!</font>

92
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:37,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I'll talk things over with Klahadore!</font>

93
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:44,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">What?! That butler went to the shore?!</font>

94
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:47,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Yeah! And he had a scary
look on his face!</font>

95
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:50,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hey, wake up!</font>

96
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:54,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">But I should still be in bed...</font>

97
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:57,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">This is no time to be sleeping!</font>

98
00:05:57,340 --> 00:05:59,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">We could be in trouble!</font>

99
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:00,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Huh?</font>

100
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:04,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I think pirates really
are going to attack us.</font>

101
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:09,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Our captain said he was lying,
but I think <i>that</i> was a lie!</font>

102
00:06:09,890 --> 00:06:11,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I think so too!</font>

103
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:15,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Me too! Something was kinda off
about the captain yesterday!</font>

104
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:17,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh, it's Miss Kaya!</font>

105
00:06:17,690 --> 00:06:19,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She's alright!</font>

106
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:32,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">She looks worried about something.</font>

107
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:35,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Miss Kaya, walking outside
all by herself...</font>

108
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:37,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Something's up!</font>

109
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:39,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Something's <i>gotta</i> be up!</font>

110
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:45,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Come forth, Meowban Brothers!</font>

